extends ../baseEmail

block content
  p Hi,
  p We received a request to reset the password for your #{payload.appInfo.name} account. We understand the importance of account security and are here to assist you in regaining access to your account.
  p To proceed with resetting your password, please use the following password reset token:

  h2
    b #{payload.user.token}

  p If you did not initiate the password reset request or if you have any concerns, please disregard this email. Your account's password will remain unchanged.

  p If you encounter any difficulties during the password reset process or if you have any questions, please contact our support team at [#{payload.appInfo.email} or #{payload.appInfo.phone}]. We are available to assist you and ensure a smooth password recovery process.

  p We highly recommend choosing a strong, unique password that is not easily guessable and keeping it confidential to protect your account.

  small Thank you for your attention to this matter. We value your security and strive to provide a seamless user experience on our platform.
  br
  small
    b - #{payload.appInfo.email}, #{payload.appInfo.name}